show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/xuQ89N
show.description: When Priya, once ridiculed for her weight, disappears from the world that shamed her, she returns years later as Avni—a bold, unrecognizable force of power. Fueled by heartbreak and reborn through resilience, Avni sets out to reclaim her worth and rewrite the rules. A gripping tale of transformation, revenge, and raw empowerment, Too Heavy to Handle is an emotional thrill ride where every wound becomes a weapon.
